Radioify for Windows
====================

This bundle contains a prebuilt Windows x64 copy of Radioify.

Install on this PC:
- Double-click install_radioify.cmd
- Or run install_radioify.ps1 from PowerShell

Portable use:
- Run radioify.exe directly from the extracted folder

What the installer does:
- Installs the full MSIX package that owns Radioify, file associations, and
  Explorer integration

Notes:
- Installing may trigger a UAC prompt to trust the development certificate
- The extracted bundle contains the signed .msix and its certificate at the
  bundle root. Manifest inputs stay under win11-explorer-integration.
- PSF2 playback still needs hebios.bin supplied separately
